features: 【Your Travel Assistant】 Gapuyer water bottle holder with shoulder strap is specially designed for Stanley Quincher H2.0 40 oz and Adventure 40 oz tumbler. It solves the trouble of carrying Stanley cup when you go out. It can accommodate the items you need to carry with you , very suitable for freeing your hands, and fits perfectly with the cup to fully protect the stanley mug. It is very suitable for commuting, jogging, hiking, going to work, school, gym and other outdoor activities.

【Multi-functional advantages】 Water bottle carrier has a detachable mobile phone wallet and shoulder strap. The enlarged mobile phone wallet has 2 pockets designed with extra large space. It can also accommodate your items (phones, lipstick, glasses, cash, cards, keys) provides ample space. The shoulder strap and mobile phone wallet combination can be used as a crossbody mobile phone wallet, and the water bottle bag can be used alone when working at home for more flexibility and practicality.

【Innovative 3D embossed fabric】water bottle pouch is made of high-quality neoprene fabric. Our innovative process heat-embosses the exquisite 3D diamond pattern on the surface. The water bottle bag is more textured, more fashionable and beautiful, and it has better anti-collision performance. Softness and elasticity effectively prevent the bottle surface from being damaged and scratched. The fabric is machine washable and easy to clean.

【Comfortable Carrying Method】 Shoulder strap is equipped with thick soft shoulder pads, and the shoulder strap can be easily adjusted from 34 in to 63 in, making it suitable for various body types. The hand strap and shoulder strap can be used together to easily switch between shoulder and hand carrying methods, and a straw cover is provided to keep the straw cover hygienic and prevent water splashing. Comes with a carabiner to carry other accessories.

【Product Guarantee】At Gapuyer, you can expect the highest quality products and unparalleled customer service. If you have any questions, please contact us, we will support you throughout the process. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 17, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great product- as described/pictured
reviews.reviewText: I love this! I received my cream colored Stanley cup from my husband last week for my birthday and I knew right away I wanted to get something I could carry it with that could also protect it. I am a mom with 4 kiddos, I’m clumsy and my kids are rambunctious lol. I wanted something that could protect incase of the inevitable falls/drops it may take in the future lol. This will serve its purpose perfectly! I love the textured finish on the neoprene type material, I love the cream and grey colors they match perfectly with my cup, I love that there are two straps one hand strap and one shoulder strap that are connected with metal connectors and have a neoprene type material grasp. I love that the strap can fit across my chest (I am a plus sized woman with a large chest) because straps tend to slide off my shoulders easily and that can become very irritating. I love the phone/money/ID/card pocket that is detachable, I feel like this will make it easier to fit into a truck cup holder without the pocket blocking it from fitting all the way. I love that this cup cover/holder makes it easier for someone to carry all their necessities and water while walking, hiking, going to the lake/pool, or even going shopping, this will work well in place of a purse. My iPhone 12 Pro Max fits perfectly into the large zipper pouch (with phone case) and still has room. I love that I can also connect my keys if need be. It’s the perfect cup accessory for on the go. And the added straw topper is adorable and serves its purpose.

reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Close-Up Video Review
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I'm a fan! I wanted to protect my 40 oz. Stanley insulated cup from scratches and dings. I also know that it's heavier and awkward to carry the cup when it's full. I was searching and found this. It's perfect! My first attraction was the purse is detachable! The video explains the details. I know white can look dirty easier, but I like the classy look. I plan to wash it in my mesh laundry bag. So far I like the quality. The only thing is the shoulder pad shifts easily so I have to adjust it so it stays on top of my shoulder. Not a deal-breaker for me at all. There is a chemical smell, but not as bad as I thought based on reviews. I like it so much, I ordered 2 more for gifts!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 20, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Not For Me
reviews.reviewText: This definitely will only work for a 40 oz Stanley or similar tumbler with the same dimensions. I had a different Stanley sleeve before this that worked for both my 24 oz Owala and To-Go Buddy, but I wanted something with a removable pocket. This did not work for either since it was too tall and the velcro only sticks to itself, it cannot stick to the material up the sides as that is too slick. I was able to use the smaller strap to get it to work with my Owala but ended up returning it because I didn't want to fuss with that all the time, plus the smell from the material was too overwhelming for me. It also started fraying immediately from the velcro because of the delicate material used along the edges. If you can get the smell out and are using this for the Stanley only, though, I thought this was really cute and liked the detachable pocket, extra strap, and black metal hardware.
